.ident	"@(#)proto:locale/C/menus/help/change_pkgs	1.11"
.related kbhelp genhelp help.main
.title Help: View or Change Package Selection
ABOUT THIS OPTION
Select the View or Change Package Selection option to list the
packages available for installation.

An asterisk (*) next to the package name indicates that the
package will be installed.

ADDING/REMOVING PACKAGES
If you want to add or remove a package from the list of
packages to install, use the arrow keys to move to the
package; then press the space bar to add or remove the
asterisk next to the package name.

If you want to select all packages, press <F5>.  If you
want to cancel all selections and restore the system
defaults, press <F6>.
                                   (CONTINUED)
.page
EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Main Menu.

EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Main Menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
